[30.277378, "o", "\r\n  The portfolio's eight projects share an event vocabulary, a\r\n"]
[30.277664, "o", "  taxonomy (OWASP / ATLAS / AI RMF), and a Splunk pipeline. Project 8\r\n  reads what the other seven produce, maps each finding to its\r\n  AI RMF subcategory, and produces continuous-monitoring evidence —\r\n  the same Q-Compliance / Q-Audit pattern, applied to AI governance.\r\n"]
